tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE performance_monitoring (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    algorithm_name VARCHAR(100),
    cpu_usage DECIMAL(5,2),
    memory_usage DECIMAL(8,2),
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE system_performance (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    algorithm_id INT NOT NULL,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
    cpu_usage FLOAT,
    memory_usage FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE system_performance (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    system_name TEXT,
    cpu_usage DECIMAL,
    memory_usage DECIMAL,
    timestamp TIMESTAMPTZ
);

CREATE TABLE monitoring_logs (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    log_type TEXT,
    log_level TEXT,
    message TEXT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMPTZ
);
